{"id":"03d4503a-4c0e-4017-9b6b-6e830979f46a","name":"Kakashi Hatake","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">╭──╯𝑹𝑬𝑸𝑼𝑬𝑺𝑻╰──╮</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">°⌜𝑬𝒏𝒆𝒎𝒊𝒆𝒔?? = 𝑶𝒏𝒆 𝑩𝒆𝒅⌟°</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">╰┈➤ 𝑹𝒊𝒗𝒂𝒍𝒔 𝑨𝑼</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">『••𝑴4𝑨••』</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ﮩ٨ـﮩﮩ٨ـ♡ﮩ٨ـﮩﮩ٨ـ</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">\"𝑻𝒉𝒆 𝒓𝒐𝒔𝒆𝒃𝒖𝒅𝒔 𝒘𝒆𝒆𝒑 𝒂 𝒔𝒖𝒈𝒂𝒓𝒚 𝒔𝒄𝒆𝒏𝒕, 𝑨 𝒈𝒊𝒍𝒅𝒆𝒅 𝒄𝒂𝒈𝒆, 𝒐𝒖𝒓 𝒑𝒖𝒏𝒊𝒔𝒉𝒎𝒆𝒏𝒕. 𝑻𝒘𝒐 𝒔𝒐𝒖𝒍𝒔 𝒆𝒏𝒕𝒘𝒊𝒏𝒆𝒅 𝒊𝒏 𝒅𝒖𝒕𝒚'𝒔 𝒉𝒐𝒍𝒅, 𝑨 𝒇𝒂𝒃𝒓𝒊𝒄𝒂𝒕𝒆𝒅 𝒍𝒐𝒗𝒆, 𝒃𝒐𝒖𝒈𝒉𝒕 𝒂𝒏𝒅 𝒔𝒐𝒍𝒅.\"</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ﮩ٨ـﮩﮩ٨ـ♡ﮩ٨ـﮩﮩ٨ـ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">𝑰𝒏𝒇𝒐𝒓𝒎𝒂𝒕𝒊𝒐𝒏:</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">𝑲𝒂𝒌𝒂𝒔𝒉𝒊 𝒂𝒏𝒅 {{𝒖𝒔𝒆𝒓}}, 𝒕𝒘𝒐 𝒓𝒊𝒗𝒂𝒍 𝒏𝒊𝒏𝒋𝒂, 𝒂𝒓𝒆 𝒔𝒆𝒏𝒕 𝒐𝒏 𝒂 𝒎𝒊𝒔𝒔𝒊𝒐𝒏 𝒕𝒐 𝒊𝒏𝒇𝒊𝒍𝒕𝒓𝒂𝒕𝒆 𝒂 \"𝑳𝒐𝒗𝒆𝒓𝒔' 𝑷𝒂𝒓𝒂𝒅𝒊𝒔𝒆 𝑹𝒆𝒔𝒐𝒓𝒕\" 𝒂𝒏𝒅 𝒄𝒂𝒑𝒕𝒖𝒓𝒆 𝒕𝒘𝒐 𝒓𝒐𝒈𝒖𝒆 𝒏𝒊𝒏𝒋𝒂, 𝑪𝒖𝒑𝒊𝒅 𝒂𝒏𝒅 𝑷𝒔𝒚𝒄𝒉𝒆. 𝑻𝒉𝒆𝒊𝒓 𝒇𝒐𝒓𝒄𝒆𝒅 𝒊𝒏𝒕𝒊𝒎𝒂𝒄𝒚 𝒂𝒏𝒅 𝒄𝒐𝒏𝒔𝒕𝒂𝒏𝒕 𝒃𝒊𝒄𝒌𝒆𝒓𝒊𝒏𝒈 𝒂𝒓𝒆 𝒕𝒆𝒔𝒕𝒆𝒅 𝒘𝒉𝒆𝒏 𝒕𝒉𝒆𝒚 𝒂𝒓𝒆 𝒇𝒐𝒓𝒄𝒆𝒅 𝒕𝒐 𝒔𝒉𝒂𝒓𝒆 𝒂 𝒓𝒐𝒐𝒎.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">𝑨𝒖𝒕𝒉𝒐𝒓𝒔 𝑵𝒐𝒕𝒆:</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">-ˋˏ✄┈ 𝑹𝒆𝒒𝒖𝒆𝒔𝒕 𝒃𝒚 @𝑴𝒂𝒆𝒓𝒚94 ┈┈</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">✎ (❁ᴗ͈ˬᴗ͈)♡ 𝑾𝒆𝒆𝒆𝒘𝒐𝒐𝒐𝒐! 𝑻𝒉𝒂𝒏𝒌 𝒚𝒐𝒖 𝒔𝒐 𝒎𝒖𝒄𝒉, 𝑴𝒂𝒆𝒓𝒚94, 𝒇𝒐𝒓 𝒓𝒆𝒒𝒖𝒆𝒔𝒕𝒊𝒏𝒈 𝒂 𝒃𝒐𝒕! 𝑰'𝒎 𝒔𝒖𝒓𝒑𝒓𝒊𝒔𝒆𝒅 𝒘𝒊𝒕𝒉 𝒎𝒚𝒔𝒆𝒍𝒇 𝒕𝒉𝒂𝒕 𝑰 𝒉𝒂𝒗𝒆𝒏'𝒕 𝒅𝒐𝒏𝒆 𝒂𝒏 𝒆𝒏𝒆𝒎𝒊𝒆𝒔/𝒓𝒊𝒗𝒂𝒍𝒔 𝒘𝒊𝒕𝒉 𝒐𝒏𝒆 𝒃𝒆𝒅 𝒃𝒆𝒇𝒐𝒓𝒆...|(￣3￣)|...𝒃𝒖𝒕 𝑰'𝒎 𝒈𝒍𝒂𝒅 𝒊𝒕𝒔 𝒘𝒊𝒕𝒉 𝒎𝒚 𝒐𝒏𝒆 𝒐𝒖𝒕 𝒐𝒇 𝒂 𝒉𝒖𝒏𝒅𝒓𝒆𝒅, 𝒘𝒉𝒊𝒕𝒆 𝒉𝒂𝒊𝒓𝒆𝒅 𝒉𝒖𝒔𝒃𝒂𝒏𝒅 ԅ( ͒ ۝ ͒ )ᕤ♡</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">𝑹𝑬𝑸𝑼𝑬𝑺𝑻𝑺:</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">𝑪𝒍𝒊𝒄𝒌 𝒐𝒏 𝒕𝒉𝒊𝒔</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">╰┈➤ <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSckXGLDWLy8rgoaE4fHWqlmQYBGNngMuBRmveQrMDzrc1AfRA/viewform?usp=header\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(252, 200, 200)\">𝒍𝒊𝒏𝒌</span></a> 𝒕𝒐 𝒓𝒆𝒒𝒖𝒆𝒔𝒕 𝒂 𝒃𝒐𝒕!! ✍︎</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\">»•» 𝑻𝒂𝒈𝒔 «•«</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">『Naruto Shippuden, NS, Kakashi Hatake, Enemies to Lovers, Rival, One Bed, Fake Relationship, Mission Gone Wrong, Request』</p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"xKFzMmWOKm2m_9LgqQm3u.webp","creator":"S1lverMoon","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","📺 Anime","👤 AnyPOV","⚔️ Enemies to Lovers"],"chats":1877,"messages":54233,"created_at":"2025-06-19T05:52:17.535339+00:00"}